bibliothek.util.xml

Class XContainer

  • java.lang.Object
    • bibliothek.util.xml.XContainer
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    XAttribute, XElement

    public class XContainer
extends Object
    An element that can have some content. The content can be a String, byte-array or a primitive value type.
    Author:
    Benjamin Sigg
